ygData.subject: RE: RE: That darn goblin alchemist.
ygData.msgSnippet: Hang in there, friend. It took me over 84 hours to complete the entire quest, including 13 hours for the Misty Alchemist, and over 64 hours for the Beholder
ygData.messageBody:
Hang in there, friend. It took me over 84 hours to complete the entire
quest, including 13 hours for the Misty Alchemist, and over 64 hours for the
Beholder Alchemist. I found the Misty Alchemist in the middle camp, although
a friend of mine found him in the Southern camp.

I wish you luck.

Praelor Dileasai
Monk of The Ashen Order

-----Original Message-----
From: RaceFace [mailto:bean@...]
Sent: Friday, February 18, 2000 12:09 AM
To: EQ-Monks@onelist.com
Subject: Re: RE: [EQ-Monks] That darn goblin alchemist.

From: "RaceFace" <bean@...>

I've now camped the middle camp for 9 hours, the single hut camp for 5 hours
(killed Mooto 9 times, warrior 6 times, shaman once).. and have not seen the
alchemist. This is getting frustrating, since this is supposed to be the
"short" camp.

Did the alchemist appear at the middle camp or did he walk over?

-- Raean "Really Sleepy" Bloodyhands, 26th circle, Tunare.

> Personally, I camped the single tent camp for 9 hours with no luck. Killed
> Mooto many, many times. Moved to the middle camp and killed the Alchemist
> within 45 minutes. This was Sunday, btw.
>
> Praelor Dileasai
